    • Field Detail

      • QUERY_HINTS

        static final String QUERY_HINTS
        An optional Properties object specifying query hints which apply to this AST node.

        The relationship between SPARQL level query hints, the annotations on the ASTBase and PipelineOp nodes is a bit complex, and this Properties object is a bit complex. Briefly, this Properties object contains property values which will be applied (copied) onto generated PipelineOps while annotations on the ASTBase nodes are interpreted by IASTOptimizer s and AST2BOpUtility. SPARQL level query hints map into one or another of these things, or may directly set attributes on the AST2BOpContext.

        See Also:
        ASTQueryHintOptimizer, Clean up query hints , Constant Field Values
